To view which version of node you're using:
    node --version


To view all version of node which you can download:

    nvm ls-remote


To view all verison of node currently installed:

    nvm ls

To install a specific version of node:

    nvm install 8.6.0 (or whatever version)


To use a specific version of node:

    nvm use 8.6.0 (or whatever version)


